Area_c = \pi r^2
Area_s = 4r^2
Area_c + Area_s = 10
(\pi r^2) + (4r^2) = 10
{\operatorname{d}\over\operatorname{d}r} [(\pi r^2) + (4r^2) - 10] = 2\pi r + 8r
